The '''Master Control Computer''' was located in the [[Emperor's Citadel]] on [[Byss/Legends|Byss]]. During [[Operation Shadow Hand]] it continuously broadcast a [[Master Control Signal]] through the [[HoloNet/Legends|HoloNet]] that controlled the operations of all [[World Devastator]]s. In the [[Battle of Calamari]], [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] had [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] interfere with the signal, causing the loss of three Devastators.

